---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout lang="en" title="Privacy Policy — Davide Veneto" description="Privacy policy pursuant to GDPR for the Davide Veneto website.">
	<section class="pt-32 pb-16 md:pt-44 md:pb-24">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
			<a href="/en/" class="text-red text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase hover:text-red-glow transition-colors mb-8 inline-block">
				<svg class="inline w-4 h-4 mr-1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
				Back to home
			</a>

			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-heading mb-8">Privacy <span class="text-red">Policy</span></h1>

			<div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-6">
				<p class="text-gray-400 text-xs">Last updated: March 17, 2026</p>

				<h2 class="text-xl font-heading text-white mt-8 mb-3">1. Data controller</h2>
				<p>
					Power Adv di Veneto Davide<br />
					Strada De Regibus 1/C, 14100 Asti (AT), Italy<br />
					VAT: 01757980055<br />
					Email: <a href="mailto:davideveneto@powerads.it" class="text-red hover:text-red-glow">davideveneto@powerads.it</a>
				</p>

				<h2 class="text-xl font-heading text-white mt-8 mb-3">2. Data collected</h2>
				<p>This website collects the following data:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
					<li><strong class="text-white">Browsing data:</strong> IP address, browser type, operating system, pages visited, access time. This data is automatically collected by the systems running the website (GitHub Pages).</li>
					<li><strong class="text-white">Technical cookies:</strong> necessary for the website to function. No consent required.</li>
					<li><strong class="text-white">Third-party cookies (YouTube):</strong> this site embeds YouTube videos in privacy-enhanced mode (youtube-nocookie.com). These videos are loaded only after your explicit interaction. YouTube may set cookies to track video viewing.</li>
					<li><strong class="text-white">Voluntarily provided data:</strong> when you book a call via Calendly, the data you enter (name, email, phone) is processed by Calendly according to their own privacy policy.</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-xl font-heading text-white mt-8 mb-3">3. Processing purposes</h2>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
					<li>Service delivery and website operation</li>
					<li>Responding to contact requests</li>
					<li>Displaying video content (upon interaction)</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-xl font-heading text-white mt-8 mb-3">4. Legal basis</h2>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
					<li><strong class="text-white">Legitimate interest</strong> for browsing data and technical cookies</li>
					<li><strong class="text-white">Consent</strong> for third-party cookies (YouTube)</li>
					<li><strong class="text-white">Contractual performance</strong> for data provided via Calendly</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-xl font-heading text-white mt-8 mb-3">5. Third-party services</h2>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
					<li><strong class="text-white">GitHub Pages:</strong> website hosting. <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement" class="text-red hover:text-red-glow" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Privacy Policy</a></li>
					<li><strong class="text-white">YouTube (Google):</strong> video embedding in privacy-enhanced mode. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-red hover:text-red-glow" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
					<li><strong class="text-white">Calendly:</strong> appointment scheduling. <a href="https://calendly.com/privacy" class="text-red hover:text-red-glow" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Calendly Privacy Policy</a></li>
					<li><strong class="text-white">Google Fonts:</strong> font loading. <a href="https://developers.google.com/fonts/faq/privacy" class="text-red hover:text-red-glow" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Fonts Privacy Policy</a></li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="text-xl font-heading text-white mt-8 mb-3">6. Data retention</h2>
				<p>Browsing data is retained only for the time strictly necessary for website operation. Third-party cookies have variable durations according to the respective providers' policies.</p>

				<h2 class="text-xl font-heading text-white mt-8 mb-3">7. Your rights</h2>
				<p>Under Articles 15-22 of the GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
					<li>Access your personal data</li>
					<li>Request rectification or deletion</li>
					<li>Restrict or object to processing</li>
					<li>Request data portability</li>
					<li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
					<li>Lodge a complaint with the Data Protection Authority</li>
				</ul>
				<p>To exercise your rights, contact us at the email address above.</p>

				<h2 class="text-xl font-heading text-white mt-8 mb-3">8. Cookies</h2>
				<p>This website uses only technical cookies necessary for operation. YouTube cookies are activated only when you click to play a video. You can manage your preferences through your browser settings at any time.</p>

				<h2 class="text-xl font-heading text-white mt-8 mb-3">9. Changes</h2>
				<p>The Data Controller reserves the right to modify this policy at any time. Changes will be published on this page with the date of the last update.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<footer class="py-8 border-t border-gray-700/30">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:justify-between md:items-center gap-4 text-center md:text-left">
				<div>
					<p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Power Adv di Veneto Davide</p>
					<p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mt-1">Strada De Regibus 1/C, 14100 Asti (AT) · P.IVA 01757980055</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<a href="/en/privacy/" class="text-gray-500 text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</footer>
</Layout>
